@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h4>Greetings, asphalt maestro and owner of "Care4YourGarage"! 🚗✨</h4>

<p>
    At "Care4YourGarage," we understand that your relationship with your car goes beyond just filling up the tank. We want you to feel as comfortable with us as in the driver's seat of your favorite vehicle. So, here's our privacy policy, designed to be as smooth as the power steering in your car.
</p>

<ol>
    <li>
        <strong>Driver Data - More Confidential than the Secret Route:</strong>
        <p>We collect information such as your music preferences for those epic road trips. Your playlist secrets are safer with us than that secret route only your car knows.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Customer Data - As Exclusive as VIP Service:</strong>
        <p>Name, address, and contact details. We treat your data more exclusively than the VIP service at a luxury car dealership. We promise not to reveal your address to broom salesmen!</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Appointments - Reserved for Your Star Car:</strong>
        <p>We schedule appointments to pamper your star vehicle. Your car is like a celebrity to us, and we'll only share the date and time with our talented team of car enthusiasts.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Work Orders - The Script for Transformation:</strong>
        <p>Details about repairs and enhancements. We consider this section the script for your car's transformation. We'll only share these details with our team of mechanics, our true motor wizards!</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Invoices - Easier to Understand than a Repair Manual:</strong>
        <p>Payment information and invoice details. Our invoices are easier to understand than a repair manual. Don't worry; we don't expect you to be a finance expert—we want you to focus on enjoying the journey!</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Company Expenses - Where We Spend Less on Coffee and More on Tools:</strong>
        <p>Details of company expenses. We'll reveal the secrets of our expenses only to our accountants and the pizza delivery guy who always asks if we need help under the hood.</p>
    </li>
</ol>

<p>
    <strong>Security and Confidentiality:</strong>
    Your information is as secure as a car in an alarm-equipped garage. We use cutting-edge security technologies, and our employees have taken an oath of confidentiality as serious as a mechanic with a wrench.
</p>

<p>
    Thank you for choosing "Care4YourGarage" to pamper your beloved vehicle! If you ever need maintenance advice or just want to talk about the latest car model, we're here for you!
</p>

<p>
    With a passion for engines,
    The "Care4YourGarage" Team 🛠️🚗
</p>
